---
import background from "../assets/background-hero-image.png";
---

<section id="container" class="h-svh">
	<div class="w-full h-full bg-black -z-10 absolute">
		<img
			src={background.src}
			alt="Casas modulares"
			class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60"
		/>
	</div>
	<div class="flex h-full md:pt-16 p-4 md:p-4">
		<div
			class="m-auto flex flex-col gap-8 items-center md:gap-20 md:px-10 lg:gap-10 lg:items-start"
		>
			<h1
				class="text-5xl text-[#F5F5F5] font-bold text-center md:text-8xl md:text-left"
			>
				CASAS MODULARES
			</h1>
			<p
				class="text-xl text-[#F5F5F5] w-[20rem] md:text-5xl md:w-full lg:w-4/5 lg:text-3xl"
			>
				Ekomod es nuestra solución para quienes buscan construir rápido,
				con calidad y diseño flexible. Nuestras casas modulares son
				ideales para zonas turísticas o cualquier terreno donde se
				quiera optimizar el espacio y rentabilizar la inversión.
			</p>
			<button
				id="scroll-to-contact"
				class="text-2xl text-white border-4 border-[#F5F5F5] rounded-xl p-4 font-bold cursor-pointer md:text-5xl md:p-8 md:self-start md:px-10 lg:text-4xl lg:font-normal lg:p-6 lg:w-92"
			>
				Contactanos
			</button>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	@media screen and (min-width: 1230px) and (max-width: 1440px) {
		h1 {
			font-size: 4rem;
		}
		p {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}
		button {
			font-size: 2rem;
			padding: 1rem 2rem;
			width: 20rem;
		}
	}
</style>

<script>
	document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
		document
			.getElementById("scroll-to-contact")
			?.addEventListener("click", () => {
				document
					.getElementById("contact-us")
					?.scrollIntoView({ behavior: "smooth" });
			});
	});
</script>
